column14: 200 Hz 100% looks tuned for day0 but not for the rest. Did we lose the neuron?
Looks like it was present on the first day and lost on later ones
Strange phenomenon in 10Hz, 100% where multiple peaks occur in second day
200Hz is tuned for all depths. 20 and 10Hz are tuned only at lower depths
Tuning at 200Hz appears to decrease and eventually is lost across the days
Mostly noisy, but 0Hz, 0% plot is interesting in that it transitions from excitatory on first day to clearly inhibitory on the later two
